for additional resources.

5
00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:17.150
Hey. Chief Springer.

6
00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:18.880
This isn't your dirt.

7
00:00:19.010 --> 00:00:20.180
The winds could change.

8
00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:22.190
