right towards us.

9
00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:23.620
You keep the fire
on your side of the dirt.

10
00:00:23.720 --> 00:00:26.060
you keep command.
but you couldn't do that.

11
00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:29.020
Chief Manuel Perez.
Assuming County Line I.C.

12
00:00:29.130 --> 00:00:30.530
Let's get to work. gentlemen.
Let's move!

13
00:00:30.630 --> 00:00:32.360
- Hell yeah. Cap!
- Let's go! Cut this line!

14
00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:33.960
Go! Move! Move!

15
00:00:34.060 --> 00:00:36.130
We still got a shot.
You got a fast way for us to get

16
00:00:36.230 --> 00:00:37.500
back down to that line?

17
00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:39.140
Watch out!

18
00:00:41.970 --> 00:00:43.740
Jake. check in. damn it.

19
00:00:43.870 --> 00:00:45.440
Manny. where is Tyler?

20
00:00:45.540 --> 00:00:46.740
And where's Bode?

21
00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:49.080
Fire's coming! Get down!

22
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.074
