23
00:00:59.790 --> 00:01:01.820
Keep breathing. Tyler.

24
00:01:02.690 --> 00:01:03.990
Keep breathing.

25
00:01:05.590 --> 00:01:08.400
Close to the dirt
as you can get!

26
00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:13.400
Firefighter Leone. I.C.

27
00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:15.370
Come in. Over.

28
00:01:15.470 --> 00:01:19.180
I repeat. Leone. come in. Over.

29
00:01:19.980 --> 00:01:22.610
A price was paid
for the County Line Fire.

30
00:01:22.710 --> 00:01:24.710
A firefighter's career
may be over.

31
00:01:24.810 --> 00:01:26.620
